OL,3,CNew dads call for better paternity
OL,4,Cleave
OL,6,FNew fathers in Oxfordshire say current
OL,7,Fpaternity rights are outdated and need
OL,8,Fto be changed to support working
OL,9,Ffamilies.
OL,11,FCurrently employees are eligible for
OL,12,Fup to two weeks statutory paternity
OL,13,Fleave and statutory pay of just over
OL,14,F#187 a week - if they've worked for at
OL,15,Fleast 26 weeks. There's no entitlement
OL,16,Ffor self-employed fathers.
OL,18,FStatutory maternity leave on the the
OL,19,Fother hand is 52 weeks.
