OL,3,CNew dads call for better paternity
OL,4,Cleave
OL,6,FNow campaign group, The Dad Shift, is
OL,7,Fcalling for change. They say they want
OL,8,Flonger, affordable and equal leave for
OL,9,Fboth parents in every relationship -
OL,10,Fsame sex, heterosexual or adoptive.
OL,11,FThey also want paternity rights for
OL,12,Fself-employed people.
OL,14,FCo-founder of The Dad Shift, Alex
OL,15,FLloyd Hunter, from Oxford, said that
OL,16,Fpaternity leave in the UK is a lot
OL,17,Fshorter than in other counties.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
