OL,3,CNew dads call for better paternity
OL,4,Cleave
OL,6,FHe said: " It's also really poorly
OL,7,Fpaid. It's about 40 per cent of the
OL,8,Fminimum wage, which is below the
OL,9,Fpoverty line if that was your salary.
OL,11,F"It's not enough for people to live
OL,12,Fon, so that means you find that about
OL,13,Fa third of people take no paternity
OL,14,Fleave at all. About half of those who
OL,15,Fdo, end up in financial hardship as a
OL,16,Fresult, and it has problems short term
OL,17,Ffor families and long term.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
