OL,3,CNew dads call for better paternity
OL,4,Cleave
OL,6,F"In the short term it means mothers
OL,7,Fare left with no support while they
OL,8,Fare still recovering from birth,
OL,9,Fperhaps if they had a C-section that
OL,10,Fcould take six weeks, and they are
OL,11,Fleft on their own after two, and also
OL,12,Fwhen they are most at risk of post-
OL,13,Fnatal depression.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
