OL,3,CNew dads call for better paternity
OL,4,Cleave
OL,6,F"It also robs fathers and non birthing
OL,7,Fparents of the time they need to bond
OL,8,Fwith their child. and that has long-
OL,9,Fterm repercussions in terms of how the
OL,10,Ffamily parents, in terms of how strong
OL,11,Fthat relationship will be between
OL,12,Ffathers and their children, and the
OL,13,Fchildren, if they have that strong
OL,14,Frelationship, there's loads of
OL,15,Fevidence that they'll grow up to be
OL,16,Fhappier, do better at school and will
OL,17,Fbasically be well-rounded people if
OL,18,Fthey have that close relationship with
OL,19,Fboth parents. "
