OL,3,CNew dads call for better paternity
OL,4,Cleave
OL,6,FNew Dad, Ross Murray from Wallingford,
OL,7,Fstarted a new job shortly before his
OL,8,Fdaughter Lydia was born and so he
OL,9,Fwasn't entitled to statutory paternity
OL,10,Fleave and pay.
OL,12,FHe said: "In my case because I started
OL,13,Fa new job I wasn't eligible for paid
OL,14,Fpaternity leave. I took two weeks
OL,15,Funpaid but for some other people that
OL,16,Fwouldn't be an option.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
