OL,3,CNew dads call for better paternity
OL,4,Cleave
OL,6,F"At the moment things aren't equal.
OL,7,FSo, my wife was entitled to 12 months
OL,8,Fand I was entitled to two weeks. I
OL,9,Fwould like to be as much of a parent
OL,10,Fto our daughter as she is able to be,
OL,11,Fbut the policy stops there at the
OL,12,Fmoment."
OL,14,FMany companies offer enhanced
OL,15,Fpaternity benefits and couples have
OL,16,Fthe option of shared parental leave.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
