OL,3,CNew dads call for better paternity
OL,4,Cleave
OL,6,FA Government spokesperson from the
OL,7,FDepartment for Business and trade
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our Plan for Change is on the
OL,9,Fside of working parents, which is why
OL,10,Fwe are making Paternity Leave and
OL,11,FUnpaid Parental Leave day one rights
OL,12,Funder the Employment Rights Bill.
OL,14,F"We're also committed to carrying out
OL,15,Fa review of the parental leave system
OL,16,Fto ensure it best supports working
OL,17,Ffamilies."
