OL,3,CNew dads call for better paternity
OL,4,Cleave
OL,6,FThe day-one reform will cover leave,
OL,7,Fbut not pay. It's expected to come in
OL,8,Fin 2026 and the Government said
OL,9,Fconsideration will be given to
OL,10,Fbusinesses that might need more time
OL,11,Fto prepare for change.
OL,13,FAlex Lloyd Hunter said: "It's welcome.
OL,14,FThere are tens of thousand of people
OL,15,Fwho'll get that time who don't have it
OL,16,Fnow but that leave without pay is not
OL,17,Fmuch good because it locks the vast
OL,18,Fmajority of people out.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
